au.edu.jcu.v4l4j
Class ResolutionInfo.DiscreteResolution

java.lang.Object
  au.edu.jcu.v4l4j.ResolutionInfo.DiscreteResolution
Enclosing class:
ResolutionInfo
public static class ResolutionInfo.DiscreteResolution
extends java.lang.Object

This class represents a possible resolution supported by a video device. It also contains information on supported frame intervals at this resolution, encapsulated in a FrameInterval object returned by the getFrameInterval() method.
A ResolutionInfo.DiscreteResolution object is not instantiated directly. Instead, a list of supported ResolutionInfo.DiscreteResolutions for a given video device can be obtained through a ResolutionInfo for that device.

gilles
